You need XAMMP.
You need MySQL.

Move files in the right folder.
Employees.txt
Kawasaki.txt
Create a file in the C then create a file name 0.
Move the two text files.

Then move the HTML and PHP files.
Department.php
Efficiency.php
Employee.php
Running.php
KawasakiFrontPage.html
Runnning.html
Efficiency.html
To Htdocs where the XAMMP files is located.

Then run the txt files to the MySQL
source c:/0/Employees.txt
source c:/0/Kawaski.txt

Start the XAMMP.

Open a browswer type http://LocalHost/...
KawasakiFrontPage is to both enter either running numbers or new employee.

